<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4590587>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Halicyclops uncus new species, female. (A) Habitus, dorsal; (B) urosome with P5, dorsal; (C) urosome, ventral; (D) fourth urosomite, anal somite and left caudal ramus, dorsal; (E) middle caudal setae; (F) antennule, ventral; (G) antenna, posterior; (H) mandible, anterior. A, non-type from Midori-kawa River; B–D, F–H, holotype; E, paratype." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590587/files/figure.png" .

